id: 2463
name: Motion of No Confidence
power: 2
text: |
  Any player CAN, with Agoran consent, cause the office of Prime
  Minister to become vacant, provided that the message in which e
  does so contains the string "MOTION OF NO CONFIDENCE" in its
  subject line. Motions of no confidence SHOULD be used whenever
  Agorans want to shake things up, rather than as a personal
  judgement of the Prime Minister.
